A ƙarshe, kwallon ya sauka don Kofin Arrizabalaga yayin da ya yi tsalle kuma ya jefa kwallon cikin raga.
"Na yi kokarin zuwa wurin kuma in kama kwallon kuma 'yan wasa kamar Shaq suna wasa a duk lokacin da zai yiwu, don haka na yi kokarin samar da lokaci mai yawa da kaina", in ji Sturridge ga LiverpoolFC.com.
Na ga Kante ya zo ya tambayi kwallon ba tare da tunani sosai game da shi, kawai je game da shi.
A baya bayan nan, Chelsea ta ci 1-0 bayan Eden Hazard, tauraron Belgium, ya ci kwallaye a minti na 25.
Dan wasan Chelsea ya sake buga kwallon a hannun Mateo Kovacic a wannan lokacin, kafin ya juya kusa da tsakiyar filin kuma ya yi tsalle a cikin rabin Liverpool.
Kovacic ya ba da bas cicio da kuma tafiya da sauri a tsakiyar filin.
Sai kuma, ball ya ci gaba da gudu a tsakanin sauran 'yan wasan, inda Hazard ya jagoranci boxer.
Hazard ya kasance mai tsaron gida kuma ya ƙare a cikin babban matsayi tare da kyakkyawan hagu na hagu ya wuce Alisson Becker, daya daga cikin 'yan wasan Liverpool.
