LeBron ya buga wasan farko na Lakers a ranar Lahadi a San Diego
Ana jiran kusan ƙarshen magoya baya da ke ɗokin ganin LeBron James ya fara wasa don Los Angeles Lakers.
Luke Walton, kocin Lakers, ya sanar da cewa James zai buga wasan budewa na gasar kafin a fara kakar wasa a ranar Lahadi a San Diego.
Amma bai yanke shawarar game da nawa minti zai yi wasa sake.
Za a sami fiye da ɗaya amma ƙasa da 48, Walton ya ce a shafin yanar gizon Lakers.
Dan wasan Lakers Mike Trudell ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa zai iya yiwuwa James ya yi wasa na 'yan mintoci kaɗan.
Bayan wani aiki na farko a makon, an tambayi James game da shirye-shiryensa na Lakers na wasanni shida kafin lokacin.
