Lokacin da West Virginia Trump Rally, YouTube Channel
Shugaba Trump ya fara jerin zanga-zangar yakin neman zabe a Wheeling, West Virginia a yau.
Wannan shi ne farkon jerin jerin biyar da aka shirya don mako mai zuwa, ciki har da ziyara da kuma wuraren da suka dace kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da aka yi watsi da zaben da aka yi na tabbatar da zabarsa na Kotun Koli, Trump na neman samun goyon baya ga zaben tsakiyar lokaci saboda 'yan Republican na cikin hadarin rasa ikon da ke cikin majalisar dokokin kasar lokacin da za a yi zaben a watan Nuwamba.
A lokacin da Trump zai yi a West Virginia yau da dare da kuma yadda za a iya duba shi online?
Ana gudanar da taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia a karfe 7 na yamma Eastern Time, Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ka iya kallon wasan kwaikwayon Trump a West Virginia a kan layi a ƙasa ta amfani da tashar YouTube.
Trump na iya tattauna a wannan makon game da zabensa na Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya yi matukar damuwa sakamakon zargin da ake yi na cin zarafin jima'i da aka yi masa a majalisar dokoki da aka dakatar da shi har zuwa mako guda yayin da FBI ke bincike.
Amma babban burin jerin zanga-zangar shine taimakawa 'yan Republican masu tsananin ƙarfi a cikin zaɓen watan Nuwamba don samun ɗan ƙarfafa.
Saboda haka, yakin neman zaben Shugaba Trump ya ce za a yi zanga-zangar biyar a mako mai zuwa da nufin tayar da masu sa kai da magoya baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke neman karewa da kuma kara yawan rinjaye a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai, a cewar Reuters.
"Sarrafawa a kan majalisar dokoki na da muhimmanci sosai a kan al'amuran har sai shugaban ya yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da yawa kafin lokacin yakin neman zabe ya fara", wani mai magana da yawun yakin Trump, wanda bai bayyana sunansa ba, ya shaida wa Reuters.
Ana gudanar da wasan a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, ana iya ganin cewa wasan na yau zai zo da magoya bayan Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma ya sami labarin kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump zai ziyarci West Virginia a karo na biyu a watan da ya gabata, inda ya samu sama da maki 40 a shekarar 2016.
Trump na neman taimakon dan takarar majalisar dokoki na Jam'iyyar Republican ga West Virginia Patrick Morrisey, wanda ke baya a cikin manyan filayen.
"Ba wata alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrissey cewa shugaban ya zo nan don ya yi kokarin ba shi wani tasiri a cikin ƙwallon ƙafa", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
