Amma, Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya fada wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Alhamis: "Ya kamata a tilasta wa Majalisar Tsaro ta sanya takunkumi da kuma rashin amfani har sai mun tabbatar da cewa an kammala kawar da makaman nukiliya.
Majalisar Tsaro ta tsawaita takunkumi kan Koriya ta Arewa a matsayin daidaituwa a shekara ta 2006 don ƙoƙarin rage kudade ga shirye-shiryen nukiliya da kuma ayyukan Pyongyang.
Ri ya gana da Pompeo a babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya sannan ya ce zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe domin shirya taron na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekara, amma ba a yi tafiya ba.
Ya bar Pyongyang a watan Yuli yana cewa an samu ci gaba, amma Koriya ta Arewa ta zarge shi cikin sa'o'i da yawa na yin ayyukan da suka dace a matsayin gangster.
