Wani mai tsara yanar gizo na duniya yana shirin fara sabon intanet don samun damar shiga Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, mai kirkiro Yanar Gizo na Duniya, ya fara sabon kamfani wanda zai yi kokarin yin gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Wani sabon shiri na mai fasahar fasaha, Inrupt, wani kamfani ne wanda ke gina kan dandamali na Berners-Lee Solid open source.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda ake adana bayanan su da kuma wanda zai iya samun damar yin amfani da su.
A wata hira da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya bayyana cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce ta mallaki duniya.
Ya kamata mu yi shi yanzu, ya ce game da kamfanin.
Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don ba mutane damar ƙirƙirar bayanan sirri na kan layi ko POD.
Wannan na iya haɗa da jerin sunayen abokan hulɗa, jerin ayyukan da za a yi, kalandar, ɗakin karatu na kiɗa da sauran albarkatun mutum da na sana'a.
Yana da kamar Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna samuwa a kan daya na'ura mai kwakwalwa da kuma na'ura mai kwakwalwa a lokaci guda.
Abin da ke da ban sha'awa game da bayanan sirri na kan layi shi ne cewa yana da cikakken mai amfani wanda yake so ya ga irin bayanin da ake samu.
Kamfanin yana kira shi bayanan sirri ta hanyar bayanai.
Manufar Inrupt, a cewar Shugaba John Bruce, ita ce kamfanin ya kawo albarkatu, matakai da kuma basira masu dacewa don taimakawa wajen tabbatar da cewa Solid yana samuwa ga kowa.
A halin yanzu, kamfanin ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro daga IBM, masu haɓaka da suka yi kwangila don aiki a kan aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu sa kai.
Tun daga farkon wannan makon, masu bunkasa fasaha a duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen kansu ta amfani da albarkatun da ke samuwa a shafin Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce ba shi da wata ƙungiya da ke magana da Facebook da Google game da gabatar da canji gaba ɗaya inda ake yin amfani da tsarin kasuwancin su gaba ɗaya a cikin dare.
Ba mu nemi yardarsu.
A cikin wani rubutu a kan Medium da aka buga a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma yanayin halittu don taimakawa kare daidaito da ingancin sabon gidan yanar gizon da aka kirkira akan Solid.
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya sake fasalin Intanet lokacin da ya kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar gizo ta Duniya a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
