Da aka katse hanyoyin sadarwa, jami'an ceto ba su sami wani bayani daga tsinkayar Donggala ba, wani yanki a arewacin Palu wanda ya fi kusa da saman girgizar kasa mai girman 7.5.
A Palu, an yi wa mutane fiye da 16,000 gudun hijira bayan girgizar ƙasa da ta afku.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, a Sulawesi:
Palu ita ce babban birnin yankin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, a ƙarshen wani bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da kimanin yawan jama'a 379,800 a 2017.
Birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami.
Donggala wani babban fili ne wanda ya shimfiɗa sama da 300km (180 mil) na gabar teku a arewa maso yammacin Sulawesi.
A shekarar 2017, yankin da ake kula da shi a karkashin kasa mai suna Pride yana da yawan mutanen da suka kai 299,200.
Gidaje da gona sune manyan masu ba da gudummawa ga tattalin arzikin yankin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, musamman yankin Donggala na gabar teku.
Ana yin aikin hakar nickel a ƙasar, amma yawancin aikin yana faruwa a Morowali, a gefen tsibirin.
A cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, tsunami ya addabi Palu da Donggala sau da yawa, a cewar Hukumar Kula da Tsuntsaye ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Wani tsunami kuma ya afkawa yammacin Donggala a shekarar 1996, inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana zaune a kan Pacific seismic Fire Circle kuma tana fuskantar girgizar ƙasa a kai a kai.
Ga wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a gabar yamma ta yankin Aceh a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya shafi ƙasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: Wani mummunan girgizar ƙasa ya afkawa yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Ya mutu daruruwan a Nias Island, daga bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai girma 6.8 ta afkawa kudu da Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta jawo tsunami da ya afkawa kudu da gabar tekun, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai girman 7.6 ta afkawa kusa da garin Padang, babban birnin yankin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 sun mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai girman 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai, daga Sumatra, ta jawo tsunami mai tsayi na mita 10 da ya lalata ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Girgizar ƙasa ta buga yankin Pidie Jaya a Aceh, ta haifar da lalacewa da tsoro yayin da aka tunatar da mutane game da lalacewar girgizar ƙasa da tsunami mai haɗari a 2004.
Ba a yi tsunami ba a wannan lokacin, amma an kashe mutane fiye da 100 a sakamakon rushewar gine-gine.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai girma ta afkawa Lombok, tsibirin tsibirin Indonesia, ta kashe mutane fiye da 500, mafi yawansu a gefen arewacin tsibirin.
