Masu binciken tarayya suna neman tsauraran hukunci ga mutumin da ake zargi da kai mummunan harin a birnin New York
Masu neman shari'ar tarayya a New York suna neman tsauraran hukunci ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da mummunan harin da ya yi a New York City wanda ya kashe mutane takwas - hukuncin da ba a taɓa yi a jihar ba saboda aikata laifi na tarayya tun 1953.
An zargi Saipov, mai shekaru 30, da amfani da motar haya daga Home Depot don kai hari a kan titin bikes a kan babbar hanyar West Main Street a Manhattan Isaf, yana bugi masu tafiya da kuma masu hawa keke da ke kan hanyarsa a watan Oktoba.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu bin sa ya kamata su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas da gangan kuma ya yi mummunan rauni a jiki, bisa ga gargadi na niyyar neman hukuncin kisa, wanda aka shigar a yankin kudancin New York.
Wadannan kotuna biyu za su iya ba da hukunci mai tsanani, bisa ga takardun kotu.
Bayan 'yan kwanaki bayan harin, kotun tarayya ta tuhumi Saipov da laifin 22 wanda ya hada da laifin kisan kai don yaudara, laifin da ake amfani da shi ta hanyar masu bin doka a lokuta na aikata laifuka, da laifin tashin hankali da lalata motocin.
Masu bin sun ce harin ya bukaci babban shiri da shiri, suna bayyana harin Saipov a matsayin na lalata, mummunan da kuma lalata.
Safullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi wa dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco rauni, rauni da asarar", in ji sanarwar da gangan.
Biyar cikin wadanda aka kashe 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga kasar.
Wani ɗan shekara ya riga ya wuce zuwa Yankin Yammacin New York don gabatar da mummunan hukunci.
An yanke wa Khalid Barnes hukuncin kisa kan kisan wasu masu sayar da miyagun kwayoyi biyu amma an yanke masa hukuncin kisa a watan Satumba na 2009.
A shekarar 1953 ne aka yi wa wani ɗan'uwa da matarsa Julius da Ethel Rosenberg hukuncin kisa a New York, bayan an yanke musu hukuncin kisa a kan laifin yin leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin yakin da ya yi shekaru biyu da suka shige.
An kashe su biyu a wata wutar lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, dan kasar Uzbekistan, bai nuna nuna damuwa ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, a cewar takardun kotu.
Ya gaya wa masu bincike cewa yana jin daɗin abin da ya yi, in ji 'yan sanda.
Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa an yi masa wahayi ne ya kai harin bayan ya kalli bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa, a cewarsa.
Ya kuma nemi a sanya wata tutar ISIS a dakinsa a asibiti, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya yi ikirarin aikata laifi a kan zargin da ake masa na 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin masu kare kare kare kai da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce sun yi matukar takaici da hukuncin da aka yanke.
"Muna ganin cewa yanke shawarar neman tsauraran hukunci maimakon karbar laifin rai a kurkuku ba tare da yiwuwar sake shi ba ya sa wadannan abubuwan da suka faru su zama abin bala'i ga duk wanda ya shafi su", in ji Patton.
Kungiyar kare lafiyar Saipov ta riga ta nemi masu bin ta kada su nemi tsauraran hukunci.
